                                                                                             NIST SP 800-53A, REV. 5                         ASSESSING SECURITY AND PRIVACY CONTROLS IN INFORMATION SYSTEMS AND ORGANIZATIONS




                                                                                              PM-20(01)       DISSEMINATION OF PRIVACY PROGRAM INFORMATION | PRIVACY POLICIES ON
                                                                                                              WEBSITES, APPLICATIONS, AND DIGITAL SERVICES
                                                                                                              ASSESSMENT OBJECTIVE:
                                                                                                              Determine if:

                                                                                                              PM-20(01)[01]         privacy policies are developed and posted on all external-facing websites;

                                                                                                              PM-20(01)[02]         privacy policies are developed and posted on all mobile applicaons;

                                                                                                              PM-20(01)[03]         privacy policies are developed and posted on all other digital services;

                                                                                                              PM-20(01)(a)[01]      the privacy policies are wrien in plain language;

                                                                                                              PM-20(01)(a)[02]      the privacy policies are organized in a way that is easy to understand and navigate;
